## Welcome
---
The integration of online payments through Midtrans is easy. You can immediately accept different online payment methods from your customers. Please see the available products and methods below:

### [SNAP](/en/snap/integration.html)
	
SNAP is a payment portal that allows merchant to use Midtrans payment system, the Midtrans payment will pop-up on your checkout page. Setup is easy and there is no monthly fees, suitable for small and medium scale businesses. Please refer to this [link](https://demo.midtrans.com) for demo.

