### [Mobile](https://mobile-docs.midtrans.com)

Midtrans believes in the future of mobile first development on the e-commerce sector. Merchants who primarily conduct business through iOS and GooglePlay apps can now utilize our service to process transaction.

![mobile step](welcome/steps_mobile.png){: .img-responsive .img-thumbnail}

### [Core API](https://api-docs.midtrans.com)

Core API is a RESTful Web Service served as a communication bridge between merchant and our payment channels. Setup is easy and available for a minimum monthly fees, suitable for medium-scale enterprises.

